HW2: Lorenz Attractor

Dilara Madinger
CSCI4229/5229 Fall 2017

Three dimensional visualization of the Lorenz Attractor.
Based on class exercise - ex6.

Key bindings
arrows Change view angle
0      Reset view angle
2	Switch on the option for enlarging the graph.
+	Enlarge the graph in the x direction.
-	Shrink the graph in the x direction. 
ESC    Exit
